|in loro essere intero~): these are the angels and the heavenly spheres
(|il paese sincero~).  What the four elements and all things made of them
(in other words, all sublunar objects) are at any given instant (including
the instant of first creation) depends on other created things, namely
the causal-formative influence embodied in the stars and angels (note the
word |fanno~: sublunar things are not 'created in their entirety' because
they are also made and generated). Hence one cannot have a sublunar
