move in time and in fact generate time, but they are immune to time:
they are aeviternal". Le sfere sono il ^medium~ tra l'Intelletto e la
^fluitans materia~. Nel poema divengono un emblema di salvezza: questa
"is to be able to live within time, as a mortal creature subject to,
and with a character and physical attributes completely determined by,
the order of nature (the stars), and yet to transcend time and nature,
