one reason why the souls of the blessed appear to the pilgrim within
the spheres that determined their character, dispositions, and earthly
destiny, although they 'live in' and are not 'other than' the Empyrean"
(^The Metaphysics of Dante's ~Comedy, Oxford UP, 2005, pp. 123-24).

